{"tid":1349921,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[招腎] 係時候要統戰藍絲","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:31:46.000Z","uid":256407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df81b043642dcd4db8479e65c19e7b2930f06461","tid":1349921,"uid":256407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"身為元朗區居民，家中深藍老母俾班白衫嚇到就瀨尿，開始有少少動搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一時間知好多朋友返到屋企要同班廢中廢老大戰<br />\n依家諗緊趁機整個十八種藍絲的急救應對懶人包(非屋輩圖，要思想滲透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，但藍絲詭辯咁多，又好多人係平衡時空，啲野寫寫下發現好撚大工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無腎巴絲出黎指點下甚至加入??<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5c2cbac0ab7daadbe2ea5fe949afe59d0a6e39","tid":1349921,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}